                            <comment id="70489" author="64bitchris" created="Fri, 16 Sep 2011 04:39:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;A fix was posted on the forum - it was to revert the version of org.apache.httpcomponents:httpclient to 4.1.1 - the related issue is at &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-1118&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-1118&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="70586" author="rwinch" created="Sun, 18 Sep 2011 17:06:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is an issue with openid4java&apos;s usage of HttpClient 4.1.2. See &lt;a href=&quot;http://code.google.com/p/openid4java/issues/detail?id=162&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://code.google.com/p/openid4java/issues/detail?id=162&lt;/a&gt; To fix it I have reverted back to HttpClient 4.1.1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="124763" author="issuemaster" created="Sat, 6 Feb 2016 06:18:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue has been migrated to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-security/issues/2044&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-security/issues/2044&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
